           "instructions": "1. Cut the bagel into halves and warm them up \n   2. On boiling water, crack 2 eggs to make them poached eggs.\n   3. Prepare 1/2 avocado for platting.\n   4. Plate the bagels next to each other and Smear a thick layer of cream cheese on both halves of the warmed bagel. \n   5. Add spinach on both bagels and on top of one of  the bagels add the prepared avocado \n   6. Add the poached eggs on top of the other bagel.\n   7 Toppings = Sesame seeds on Avocado & chia seeds on poached egg.\n",
